OL,3,CPolice force become one of the first
OL,4,Cto receive domestic violence training
OL,6,FCumbria Police is set to become one of
OL,7,Fthe first forces in the country to
OL,8,Freceive specialist training regarding
OL,9,Flanguage to use when supporting
OL,10,Fvictims of domestic abuse.
OL,12,FPolice in Cumbria are now set to
OL,13,Fbenefit from 'Language Matters'
OL,14,Ftraining to combat victim-blaming
OL,15,Fvocabulary, with a focus on Violence
OL,16,FAgainst Women and Girls (VAWG).
OL,18,FSpencer from south Cumbria spoke about
OL,19,Fhis experiences in dealing with the
OL,20,Fpolice as a victim of domestic
OL,21,Fviolence.
