OL,3,CPolice force become one of the first
OL,4,Cto receive domestic violence training
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Border, he said: "It
OL,7,Fwas the most awful time of my life. I
OL,8,Fcan't think of anything worse that I
OL,9,Fhave been through or that I have heard
OL,10,Fanyone else been through.
OL,12,F"Initially it was very dismissive. I
OL,13,Fwas looked at like you are a bloke and
OL,14,Fyou should be getting on with that. I
OL,15,Fdid say to officers that was the way I
OL,16,Fwas being made to feel."
OL,18,FCumbria Police say they are committed
OL,19,Fto investigating all reports
OL,20,Fthoroughly.
