OL,3,CPolice force become one of the first
OL,4,Cto receive domestic violence training
OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "Cumbria
OL,7,FPolice takes all reports of domestic
OL,8,Fabuse extremely seriously and
OL,9,Finvestigates reports thoroughly,
OL,10,Firrespective of whether the survivor
OL,11,Freporting is male or female.
OL,13,F"Our message to victims is: 'please
OL,14,Fcome forward and have confidence in
OL,15,Freporting domestic abuse, knowing that
OL,16,Fyou can trust the support you will
OL,17,Freceive'.
