OL,3,CPolice force become one of the first
OL,4,Cto receive domestic violence training
OL,6,F"We have officers specially trained in
OL,7,Fresponding to and investigating
OL,8,Freports of domestic abuse and work
OL,9,Fclosely with partner agencies, to
OL,10,Fsafeguard victim-survivors.
OL,12,F"As a Constabulary, we have recently
OL,13,Fwelcomed independent academic scrutiny
OL,14,Fon the language used by officers and
OL,15,Fstaff. This is being followed up with
OL,16,Fbespoke training inputs and is part of
OL,17,Fa series of measures to improve the
OL,18,Fservice we offer to victims."
