OL,3,CPolice force become one of the first
OL,4,Cto receive domestic violence training
OL,6,FFor Police, Fire and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner David Allen he wants to
OL,8,Fencourage domestic violence victims to
OL,9,Fcome forward.
OL,11,FHe said: "If an individual who has
OL,12,Fsurvived domestic abuse and is telling
OL,13,Fus something then that is what we
OL,14,Frecord and that is what we believe.
OL,15,FOur job is to prove or disprove and
OL,16,Fnot to cast judgement."
