OL,3,CPolice force become one of the first
OL,4,Cto receive domestic violence training
OL,6,FDr Patricia Canning Pask from
OL,7,FNorthumbria University said: "When
OL,8,Fofficers are using words like just or
OL,9,Fonly it can come across like they are
OL,10,Fminimising what the risk or experience
OL,11,Fis.
OL,13,F"The sessions cover good and bad
OL,14,Fexamples of language, helping officers
OL,15,Funderstand the impact of their words
OL,16,Fwhen speaking to survivors."
OL,18,FHelp and support available if you are
OL,19,Fa victim of domestic violence
